Name: Voxel Printer
About the game: Voxel Printer is the voxel art crafting game similar to Minecraft that up to 12 players compete with building cubes. Create a your work that fits topic within the time given. There is a voting for the best work after the round is over. The work with the most votes wins the game. You can also extract your work as an FBX file. And please use your masterpiece in several places.
